data.description: On a quiet cul-du-sac under the majestic oaks of Richmond Hill's desirable Tranquilla Hall community, this artfully landscaped, executive home features 4-bedrooms, 3-full baths, 2379 sq ft & a giant .77 acre lot! Open floor plan. Vinyl plank flooring & crown molding throughout living areas. In the living room, an exquisite brick fireplace & floor to ceiling windows welcoming natural sunlight. Entertainer's kitchen with granite counter tops, tile backsplash, island, stainless steel appliances, pantry & breakfast area. Elegant formal dining room accented with wainscot. Main Bedroom features tray ceiling & ensuite with dual vanities, jetted tub, separate shower, & walk-in closet. 3 bedrooms including the main on the ground floor. 4th bedroom with full bath upstairs. Extensive brick patio and huge, private, fenced-in backyard backing up to woods. Spacious storage building. NEW HVAC IN 2022. Convenient to Savannah, Pooler, Fort Stewart, I-95 & Richmond Hill's best shopping and dining.
